messages.messageBody:
1/7/03 03:13:

> hey, money being given away....Me too!!!!
> Hundred dollar bills would be educational. We've never seen one before :-)
>
> Shyrley

Doesn't your monopoly set have any? ;)

I saw a 100 euro bill at the Karstadt Dept. Store over the Christmas
shopping season. The clerk thought I was going to try to steal it, I think.
My son and I started poking each other and whispering and craning our necks
to see it! (You have to understand that all the euro bills are different
colors, so the attraction was that I've never seen a bill of that color.)

Anyhow, it was funny, the look the sales clerk gave us. <g>

brenda
